OL,3,CTerminally ill Britons could move to
OL,4,CScotland for an assisted death `
OL,5,Cacademic
OL,7,FTerminally ill Britons may view
OL,8,FScotland as having a "more positive
OL,9,Fclimate" for assisted dying and could
OL,10,F"move accordingly", if legislation is
OL,11,Fpassed by Holyrood, an expert said.
OL,13,FDr Claudia Carr, an academic
OL,14,Fspecialising in medical law and ethics
OL,15,Fat the University of Hertfordshire's
OL,16,Flaw school, has been studying bills to
OL,17,Fintroduce the practice in both
OL,18,FScotland and England and Wales.
