OL,3,CTerminally ill Britons could move to
OL,4,CScotland for an assisted death `
OL,5,Cacademic
OL,7,FBut, looking at differences between Mr
OL,8,FMcArthur's proposals, and those put
OL,9,Fforward by MP Kim Leadbeater at
OL,10,FWestminster, Dr Carr said: "I'm
OL,11,Fbeginning to wonder whether some
OL,12,Fpeople will regard Scotland as a more
OL,13,Fpositive climate for an assisted death
OL,14,Fand move accordingly."
OL,16,FIf legislation is passed, the academic
OL,17,Fsaid assisted dying could come into
OL,18,Feffect in Scotland "years before it is
OL,19,Fenvisaged the law in England and Wales
OL,20,Fdoes".
