OL,5,Cacademic
OL,7,FAs a result, she said: "Anybody with a
OL,8,Fterminal diagnosis who feels the clock
OL,9,Fcounting down may well consider their
OL,10,Foptions."
OL,12,FWhile Mr McArthur's Bill requires
OL,13,Fpeople to have been resident in
OL,14,FScotland for at least 12 months before
OL,15,Fseeking to help to die, Dr Carr said
OL,16,Fthat "some people with a terminal
OL,17,Fillness ` projected to take longer
OL,18,Fthan 12 months to run its course ` may
OL,19,Fregard (that) as a reasonable period
OL,20,Fwithin which they could relocate".
