OL,7,FShe also said the definition of a
OL,8,Fterminal illness was wider in the Bill
OL,9,Fcurrently being considered by Holyrood.
OL,11,FDr Carr said: "The wording of the Bill
OL,12,Fin Scotland is wider in its definition
OL,13,Fthan the one in England and Wales."
