OL,7,FDr Carr said: "This means there is no
OL,8,Ffixed time limit for the expected
OL,9,Fdeath, and the provisions of the Bill
OL,10,Fwould apply, for example, to motor
OL,11,Fneurone disease, end stage heart
OL,12,Ffailure and advanced metastatic cancer
OL,13,F` which would likely not be the case
OL,14,Fin England and Wales."
