OL,5,Cacademic
OL,7,F"Given that the progression of a
OL,8,Fterminal condition is rarely linear,
OL,9,Fmaking such a decision would be even
OL,10,Fmore problematic."
OL,12,FMr McArthur's Bill will likely face
OL,13,Fits final vote at Holyrood early in
OL,14,F2026, though there is still the
OL,15,Fopportunity for MSPs to bring forward
OL,16,Famendments to the legislation.
OL,18,FThe Liberal Democrat MSP, however,
OL,19,Fsaid the Bill "has been a long time
OL,20,Fcoming and subject to extensive
OL,21,Fconsultation".
