OL,5,Cacademic
OL,7,FSpeaking about the legislation, Mr
OL,8,FMcArthur added: "It has been robustly
OL,9,Fdrafted, drawing on the experience of
OL,10,Fother jurisdictions where such laws
OL,11,Fhave been working safely and
OL,12,Fsuccessfully for many years.
OL,14,F"I hope that MSPs will back this
OL,15,Flegislation which balances the need
OL,16,Ffor dying people to be able to access
OL,17,Fthe option of assisted dying with
OL,18,Fstrong protections and safeguards."
